article.headline: Asbury 71, Morehead State 54
article.story: MOREHEAD, Ky. (AP) -- Ricky Minard scored 22 points to lead Morehead State to a 71-54 win over Asbury on Tuesday night. Josh Graham had nine points and 11 rebounds for the Eagles (1-1). Stephen Horn led Asbury (5-4) with 19 points, Donnie Baker scored 13 and Brad Eisert 11. Asbury came within 12 points, 48-36, with 12:47 left in the game but could get no closer. The Eagles hit 11 of their first 15 field-goal attempts, and by the 5:12 mark of the first half had built a 38-12 lead. Asbury closed to within 20 points at halftime, 42-22, with a 10-4 run.
